        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/45042098/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/45042098/" class="">第5页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2784531/" class=" " title="陈江瀚">陈江瀚</a>
                (这个人当兵去了)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="45042098">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">新思潮的优点就恰恰在于我们不想教条式地预料未来，而只是希望在批判旧世界中发现新世界。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-06-19 20:17</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>新思潮的优点就恰恰在于我们不想教条式地预料未来，而只是希望在批判旧世界中发现新世界。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

